description: Great opportunity to own a spacious one-bedroom condo, with parking, in a prime South Boston location.  This corner upper-level unit offers nice light, water views, and 640 square feet of living space.  The well-established condo association is self-managed, with low condo fees.  Deeded parking and an elevator are an added bonus! The building has common laundry, and roof access with panoramic views of the water and Downtown Boston. In proximity to bus lines, West and East Broadway restaurants, and South Boston’s beaches.
